{"type": "article", "id": 7634, "title": "Dita 穿裙子的台灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-03-23T07:05:02Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 2, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234843UbC7Ax8qaXYs21Nl.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t法国工作室 Désormeaux/carrette 和 Metylos 共同完成的这款小灯名字叫做 Dita，简单的木制底座上嵌入了灯泡，而有趣的是，他们给普通的灯泡加上了一层外衣，是一个毛毡材质的灯罩，这个像连衣裙一样的小灯罩让台灯一下子变得时尚动感了起来，而从木制平面灯具到灯罩的环绕，也展现了从二维转变到三维的时尚进程。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234840hqsFdBKjymENoQJl.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.62469438\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234840CTm5NMSbtEU8qYgR.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.62469438\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234840P0qSR3bY6cQihX98.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.62469438\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234841EFtqzUcKoDkIGR79.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.62469438\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052348412KgepS1fHlnqOVvU.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.72371638\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052348420bdzWVPytGsQf3rI.jpg\"